   {At the plate:} Left fielder Rusty Greer delivered the necessary
ground ball to score catcher Ivan Rodriguez from the third base
during the first inning. The Astros played their infield at normal
depth, and Greer put the two-strike pitch from left-hander Mike
Hampton in play. &QL;
