the first premier of the new territory of Nunavut, which came into
being Thursday in Canada's vast eastern Arctic. By Anthony DePalma.
</P>
<P>
   INDIA-EMIGRANTS (New Delhi, India) _ The Indian government this
week initiated a program that will make it easier for people of
