u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LADN-BUDGET &LR;      04-03 0138
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LADN-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following general
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Sunday, April 4, and thereafter. For questions about stories,
contact Stewart Slavin at the Daily News, (818) 713-3701.
</P>
<P>
   MCCARTHY-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ The kids are coming to Clancy's
place to sit down for a hot for Easter Sunday dinner. If it weren't
for the ragged clothes on their backs, Clancy says, they'd look
like every other kid in this city going to Easter dinner with his
parents, but these children are not that lucky. They come to
Clancy's place _ the Midnight Mission in downtown Los Angeles _
because they have no other place to go. By Dennis McCarthy. (Will
move in the ``k'' editorial, ``a'' national and ``n'' California
news files.)
</P>
</TEXT>
