<DOCNO> NYT19990403.0131 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-03 13:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4719 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MCCARTHY-COLUMN-LADN     04-03 0870
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MCCARTHY-COLUMN-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FAMILY EXTENDS GIVING SPIRIT TO EASTER FOR SKID ROW KIDS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Dennis McCarthy is a Daily News columnist) 
BY DENNIS McCARTHY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
