<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-03 14:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4728 &Cx1f; tad-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPOT-BJT04-COX     04-03 0778
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT-BJT04-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
