   GOALS-2000 _ WASHINGTON _ The nation isn't going to meet a
single one of the eight educational goals set for next year in the
``Goals 2000'' program, according to the 18-member state-federal
panel set up to monitor progress toward the goals. Some states will
fulfill some goals, but none will reach all eight. Why it happened,
and what will happen next. (Mollison, Cox News Service).
